      "review_summary": "The branch wraps Claude web fetch and app-auto web availability in a shared `--web-timeout` budget, makes provider cancellation terminal, maps Claude web timeouts to exit code 4, updates Linux auto web gating, and adds focused regression tests.\n\nReproducibility: no. live high-confidence reproduction was run because AGENTS.md warns against provider probes that can display browser-cookie or Keychain prompts. Source inspection and the linked issue show the stale Claude web auto path, and the PR adds regression tests for the bounded timeout/fallback behavior.",
